         <abstract id="aspace_adae2d2a37ed466484fb11260282634d">This collection consists of postcards and photos from 1890 to 1920 from countries and territories in Latin America and the Caribbean, including Barbados, Bermuda, Cuba, Jamaica, Martinique, Puerto Rico, Panama, Trinidad and Tobago, Venezuela, and Madeira. It also includes a small number of postcards depicting Gibraltar, photographs of the building of the Panama Canal, and artistic postcards from Chile published in 1984.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_1659023d99fe19bcfd2a756955c0e5ed">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection consists of postcards and photos from 1890 to 1920 from countries and territories in Latin America and the Caribbean, including Barbados, Bermuda, Cuba, Jamaica, Martinique, Puerto Rico, Panama, Trinidad and Tobago, Venezuela, and Madeira. It also includes a small number of postcards depicting Gibraltar, photographs of the building of the Panama Canal, and artistic postcards from Chile published in 1984.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_22b5b192e4ae0d92d863ef7cd1d37976">
